00128_112709-1-768x917.jpg 768w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112709-1-580x692.jpg 580w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112709-1-860x1027.jpg 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Attacks on political figures and Fake News<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The leading Opposition party has undergone severe threats since February 9<sup>th<\/sup>  was pronounced as the date for the twin elections in Cameroon. Many activists have taken their turns online to castigate the party and its militants. The chairman of the Social Democratic Front Ni John Fru Ndi has not been left out. His recent trip out of Cameroon has kept many tongues wagging. One infamous Facebook user wrote on his Facebook Page that the chairman may seek Assylum. Talking to the party\u2019s Deputy National Communication Secretary 3, Kejang Henry, revealed that all the allegations and insinuations about the Chairman are false. He further reiterated the statement of Ni John before he left for Europe that it was for medical control. Below are the screenshots of the fake assumptions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The story can also be found on the following link <a href=\"https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=798550453952011&amp;id=100013911900260\">https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=798550453952011&amp;id=100013911900260<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9353\" width=\"219\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732.jpg 957w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732-744x1036.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732-768x1070.jpg 768w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732-580x808.jpg 580w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112732-860x1198.jpg 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 219px) 100vw, 219px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Following the stabbing of a teacher, there was another post that the act was powered by the acts of the military. The author quoted a source from state media. however, a phone enquiry with a senior Journalist of the state media refuted the allegations. This is especially considered fake because if it had legitimacy, the source of the news would have most likely been the midday news on state media. The story would also have sparked debates and not just die down like a non-event but that has not been the case. Below is a link to the story: <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=799262700547453&amp;id=100013911900260\">https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=799262700547453&amp;id=100013911900260<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9354\" width=\"293\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756.jpg 1011w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-744x744.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-55x55.jpg 55w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-580x580.jpg 580w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-860x860.jpg 860w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112756-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 293px) 100vw, 293px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Attack on Religion<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The call for lockdown as can be seen posted on one Facebook user&#8217;s page rose tension. See screenshots below. The link to the story is also available <a href=\"https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=797938477346542&amp;id=100013911900260\">https:\/\/m.facebook.com\/story.php?story_fbid=797938477346542&amp;id=100013911900260<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112816.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9355\" width=\"213\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112816.jpg 754w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112816-744x1113.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112816-580x868.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 213px) 100vw, 213px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9356\" width=\"365\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1.jpg 1023w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1-744x729.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1-768x752.jpg 768w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1-55x55.jpg 55w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1-580x568.jpg 580w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/20200128_112839-1-860x842.jpg 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 365px) 100vw, 365px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Introduction This week&#8217;s monitoring of social media handles and groups revealed that the attacks that some individuals launched online centred on lang